# Distributions the gold corpus exercises. `cpm install -L local --cpanfile this`
# pulls each plus its full dependency closure into local/lib/perl5 — the hermetic,
# version-pinned @INC the harness queries against. Pin exact versions in
# cpanfile.snapshot (committed) so CI reconstructs the identical tree.
#
# Some dists need system libraries to build: Net::SSLeay (libssl-dev),
# XML::LibXML (libxml2-dev). CI installs those before `cpm install`.

